User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    familyName Text
    givenName Text

    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable

Issue
    subject Text
    description Textarea Maybe

    limitdate Day Maybe

    opener UserId
    createdDay Day
    createdTime TimeOfDay
    updatedDay Day
    updatedTime TimeOfDay

Channel
    type     Logic
    issue    IssueId

Ticket
    channel  ChannelId
    domain   UserId
    codomain UserId
    assign   UserId

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

Comment
    channel ChannelId
    comment Text
    speaker UserId

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

